===用法===
:image= the image to be used in the form imagename.jpg ("image:" prefix is not required)
:size= images are sized to the default of 150px if this is left blank
:caption= text that will appear if a reader moves their mouse pointer over the image
:text= the text to appear below the image, remember to wikilink relevant articles and '''bold''' the main subject
:link= the main subject article, this is the page a reader will go to when they click ''read more'', do not wikilink as this is done automatically

If there is no available image then leave image= size= and caption= blank
